@desc Make the insertion point blink and control how quickly it blinks.

If you find it difficult to see the keyboard cursor in a text field, you
can make it blink to make it easier to locate.

[steps]
* Open the $Activities; overview and start typing $gui(Universal Access).

* Click on $gui(Universal Access) to open the panel.

* Press $gui(Cursor Blinking) in the $gui(Typing) section.

* Use the $gui(Speed) slider to adjust how quickly the cursor blinks.
